{"id": 2129, "title": "Ticket #2129: LastHoldReason lost if it contains double quotes", "description": "<blockquote>\nWhen the schedd moves attributes like <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=HoldReason\" title=\"Hold Reason\">HoldReason</a></span> to <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=LastHoldReason\" title=\"Last Hold Reason\">LastHoldReason</a></span>, it doesn't do proper escaping of quotes. If the value contains a quote, then <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=LastHoldReason\" title=\"Last Hold Reason\">LastHoldReason</a></span> ends up not being set in the job ad.</blockquote>", "remarks": "<blockquote>\n</blockquote>", "derived_tickets": "", "attachments": "<html><head></head><body></body></html>", "check_ins": "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\">\n<tbody><tr><td align=\"right\" valign=\"top\" width=\"160\">2011-May-05 14:07</td>\n<td align=\"center\" valign=\"top\" width=\"30\">\n<span class=\"icon dot\">\u00a0</span></td>\n<td align=\"left\" valign=\"top\"> \nCheck-in <span class=\"chng\"><a href=\"chngview?cn=21792\">[21792]</a></span>: Fix escaping when moving <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=HoldReason\" title=\"Hold Reason\">HoldReason</a></span> to <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=LastHoldReason\" title=\"Last Hold Reason\">LastHoldReason</a></span>. <span class=\"ticket\"><a class=\"resolved\" href=\"/tickets?ticket=2129\" onclick=\"get_ticket_and_populate_wrapper('2129'); return false;\" title=\"LastHoldReason lost if it contains double quotes\">#2129</a></span> Without this fix, if a <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=HoldReason\" title=\"Hold Reason\">HoldReason</a></span> value contains a double-quote, <span class=\"wiki\"><a class=\"missing\" href=\"wiki?p=LastHoldReason\" title=\"Last Hold Reason\">LastHoldReason</a></span> ends up being unset after the job is released.  (By Jaime Frey )</td></tr>\